                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-1254" type="surname" value="RIPSHER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-1254" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY RIPSHER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the habit of dealing with Mr. Hughes—this is my brother's card, and the writing on it is the writing of the young man in his shop, but it has the name of Singleton on it, not the prisoner's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
